  "time_ut": 1657525915,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dd8 \u0db7\u0dd6\u0db8\u0dd2\u0dba\u0da7 \u0db1\u0dcf\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dba \u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0dc3\u0dd6\u0daf\u0dcf\u0db1\u0db8\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Ready to lead the motherland",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Opposition Leader Sajith Premadasa said today (11th) that he is ready to lead the program of stabilizing the country and boosting the country's economy.",
        "\"We are leading the responsibility of leading the program to stabilize the country and increase the country's economy. We appoint the government led by the President and the Prime Minister. There are no alternative solutions other than this.",
        "If anyone opposes this in the parliament and does any subversive action, we see it as an act of treason.",
        "We are ready to protect the motherland. Ready to give leadership to the motherland. Build the country's economy. Victory to the Motherland!\""
      ],
